the Book in the Library of Congress.

00:00:19.180 --> 00:00:21.580
And it's my -- thank you, thank you.

00:00:21.750 --> 00:00:22.750
[ Applause ]

00:00:25.150 --> 00:00:28.350
&gt;&gt; John Cole: It is my
pleasure to scream at you.

00:00:30.510 --> 00:00:31.510
