Later on in the program
as John told you,

00:08:12.510 --> 00:08:14.110
we are going to have a
wonderful dramatic presentation.

00:08:14.510 --> 00:08:15.976
But we need your help.

00:08:16.510 --> 00:08:16.800
Gerry, our wonderful assistant here,
