and we're going to do it --

00:14:20.550 --> 00:14:21.180
we're going to put the
authors to the test.

00:14:22.720 --> 00:14:24.520
We have a little quiz show,

00:14:25.330 --> 00:14:28.730
and if the authors could
get their bicycle horns and

00:14:28.790 --> 00:14:29.790
[ Bicycle horn]

00:14:30.790 --> 00:14:31.390
&gt;&gt; Mary Brigid: Not
through your mike --

