Joe said not through your mike.

00:14:34.790 --> 00:14:35.790
&gt;&gt; Oh, sorry.

00:14:36.790 --> 00:14:38.190
&gt;&gt; Mary Brigid: Okay.

00:14:38.790 --> 00:14:39.790
All set?

00:14:40.790 --> 00:14:41.456
&gt;&gt; Mary Brigid, can
Gerry stand in front,

