&gt;&gt; Mary Brigid: Oh,
can I stand in front?

00:14:48.790 --> 00:14:50.723
&gt;&gt; Sorry, Gerry, Gerry stand.

00:14:50.790 --> 00:14:52.056
&gt;&gt; Mary Brigid: Oh, Gerry,
can you stand in front?

00:14:52.790 --> 00:14:54.323
Okay. Gerry's going to stand
in front, and we're going

00:14:54.790 --> 00:14:58.790
to test these authors out on
